{"tid":2230781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【曙光乍現？】中國自主研發芯片見成果，84歲老太研發28nm芯片","createTime":"2020-10-05T07:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T10:52:01.000Z","uid":51665,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"f3438e802fdee57236a4cee1356ab8b169c5a2ef","tid":2230781,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:23:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/629116/%E3%80%90%E6%9B%99%E5%85%89%E4%B9%8D%E7%8F%BE%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%BB%E7%A0%94%E7%99%BC%E8%8A%AF%E7%89%87%E8%A6%8B%E6%88%90%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%8C84%E6%AD%B2%E8%80%81%E5%A4%AA%E7%A0%94%E7%99%BC28nm%E8%8A%AF%E7%89%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F629116%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%259B%2599%25E5%2585%2589%25E4%25B9%258D%25E7%258F%25BE%25EF%25BC%259F%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%258A%25AF%25E7%2589%2587%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%259E%259C%25EF%25BC%258C84%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%2599%25BC28nm%25E8%258A%25AF%25E7%2589%2587%2F&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=feeae915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/629116/%E3%80%90%E6%9B%99%E5%85%89%E4%B9%8D%E7%8F%BE%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%BB%E7%A0%94%E7%99%BC%E8%8A%AF%E7%89%87%E8%A6%8B%E6%88%90%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%8C84%E6%AD%B2%E8%80%81%E5%A4%AA%E7%A0%94%E7%99%BC28nm%E8%8A%AF%E7%89%87/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/%E8%8A%AF%E7%89%87-1-990x520.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F%25E8%258A%25AF%25E7%2589%2587-1-990x520.png&h=6b525ca3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在中美角力之間，美國連番出招，先是禁止美國公司向中資巨企華為提供芯片，繼而再嘗試壟斷國外的芯片市場。在入口芯片重重受阻的情況下，中國尚未能自主研發高端水平的芯片，這令到華為將面臨芯片短缺的情況。<br />\n<br />\n近日，有消息傳出中國一位84歲的科學家黃令儀成功自主研發到國產的高端晶片，黃老太與她的團隊成功研發名為龍芯三號的CPU 28nm晶片，這可算是中國晶片發展的里程碑，同時也是中國在被美國多方封殺下的一線曙光。<br />\n<br />\n黃老太一生的致力推動中國半導體晶片的研發和發展，在上世紀60年代畢業後，便修讀有關半導體的專科，繼而在後來的日子貢獻於中國的半導體晶片的發展，她同時亦見證了中國微電子產業的興衰。<br />\n<br />\n在2000年，本已經退休的黃老太在學生的邀請下，加入芯片製造公司龍芯，負責指導各個計畫的發展。在黃老太的指導下，公司在2002年成功研發到中國首個有自主知識產權的通用高性能微處理器，「龍芯一號」。繼而公司繼續精益求精，努力研發相關項目。現時龍芯所開發的處理器和晶片都得到廣泛應用。<br />\n<br />\n嬴國人才鼎盛邊有得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇教宗都要歸邊就知喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394a6883eb88ca727673f757db25484bf678dd60","tid":2230781,"uid":79351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"香港老早就整左龍珠晶片出黎<br />\n依家研發埋人工弱能龍心添喇<br />\n堂堂大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25eb0c435e6f3c90c77ab524c37e32d3ada52c9","tid":2230781,"uid":19527,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:29:58.000Z","msg":"龍心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00bcaabc1c5c9b7ecf26c76e9894841979d7aad6","tid":2230781,"uid":341040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:32:22.000Z","msg":"我五年前粒4790 都勁過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881eded37df87a784d3465983378144de54981b0","tid":2230781,"uid":136416,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:32:37.000Z","msg":"又係呢個阿婆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前巴打留言話google完佢<br />\n之前80幾年人生好似冇存在過<br />\n笑死"},{"pid":"70eb07ffb85c0b9716a7bd6a3d6d1bd651350b75","tid":2230781,"uid":107681,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:33:07.000Z","msg":"呀婆，d花旗參片不如你拎返屋企沖茶啦"},{"pid":"26b856dea8c033e3add75b4aa993